#: ../../slideshow_tools/presentation_tool.rst:1
msgid "Using digiKam Presentation Tool"
msgstr "Uporaba predstavitvenega orodja digiKam"

#: ../../slideshow_tools/presentation_tool.rst:1
msgid "digiKam, documentation, user manual, photo management, open source, free, learn, easy, slide, presentation, OpenGL, effects"
msgstr "digiKam, dokumentacija, uporabniški priročnik, upravljanje fotografij, odprta koda, brezplačno, učenje, enostavno, diapozitiv, predstavitev, OpenGL, učinki"

#: ../../slideshow_tools/presentation_tool.rst:14
msgid "Presentation Tool"
msgstr "Predstavitveno orodje"

#: ../../slideshow_tools/presentation_tool.rst:16
msgid "Contents"
msgstr "Vsebina"

#: ../../slideshow_tools/presentation_tool.rst:18
msgid "The **Presentation** tool creates a configurable full screen slide-show of your images using advanced visual effects."
msgstr "Orodje **Presentation** ustvari nastavljivo celozaslonsko diaprojekcijo vaših slik z uporabo naprednih vizualnih učinkov."

#: ../../slideshow_tools/presentation_tool.rst:20
msgid "With this tool you can create a perfect slide show with just three mouse clicks. When opening the tool from the :menuselection:`View --> Presentation` menu, the Presentation window **Main** page will appear asking questions as to how you want to stage your slide show. You can choose between the selected images or all images in the same album."
msgstr ""

#: ../../slideshow_tools/presentation_tool.rst:26
msgid "The Presentation Tool Dialog"
msgstr "Pogovorno okno orodja za predstavitve"

#: ../../slideshow_tools/presentation_tool.rst:28
msgid "The **Use OpenGL Transitions** checkbox enables very smooth image transitions using the OpenGL display mode. Be sure you have OpenGL enabled on your graphics card, since otherwise the slideshow will be very slow."
msgstr ""

#: ../../slideshow_tools/presentation_tool.rst:30
msgid "The **Print Filename** checkbox enables displaying the image filename in the lower left corner."
msgstr "Potrditveno polje **Natisni ime datoteke** omogoča prikaz imena slikovne datoteke v spodnjem levem kotu."

#: ../../slideshow_tools/presentation_tool.rst:32
msgid "The **Loop** checkbox will enable running the whole show in an endless loop (until manually stopped with :kbd:`Esc`)."
msgstr "Potrditveno polje **Zanka** bo omogočilo izvajanje celotne oddaje v neskončni zanki (dokler je ročno ne zaustavite z :kbd:`Esc`)."

#: ../../slideshow_tools/presentation_tool.rst:34
msgid "The **Shuffle Images** checkbox will enable displaying the images randomly (not using the current images collection order)."
msgstr "Potrditveno polje **Suffle Images** bo omogočilo naključni prikaz slik (brez uporabe trenutnega vrstnega reda zbiranja slik)."

#: ../../slideshow_tools/presentation_tool.rst:36
msgid "The **Delay Between Images** may be set in millisecond steps. 1500 milliseconds correspond to 1.5 seconds and is a good default value. The best timing depends also a bit on your computer power and the transition effect. Try it out before you show it to your friends!"
msgstr ""

#: ../../slideshow_tools/presentation_tool.rst:38
msgid "There are more than a dozen **Transition Effects** available to choose from. The **Random** selection will change the transition effect with every image."
msgstr ""

#: ../../slideshow_tools/presentation_tool.rst:40
msgid "The **Caption** page from the tool allows to customize the font properties to render item description over the screen."
msgstr "Stran **Caption** v orodju omogoča prilagoditev lastnosti pisave za upodabljanje opisa predmeta na zaslonu."

#: ../../slideshow_tools/presentation_tool.rst:46
msgid "The Caption Settings from Presentation Tool"
msgstr "Nastavitve napisov iz orodja za predstavitve"

#: ../../slideshow_tools/presentation_tool.rst:48
msgid "The **Soundtrack** page from the tool allows to append audio tracks to play while slideshow."
msgstr "Stran **Zvočni posnetek** v orodju omogoča dodajanje zvočnih posnetkov za predvajanje med diaprojekcijo."

#: ../../slideshow_tools/presentation_tool.rst:54
msgid "The Soundtrack Settings from Presentation Tool"
msgstr "Nastavitve zvočnega posnetka iz orodja za predstavitve"

#: ../../slideshow_tools/presentation_tool.rst:56
msgid "The **Advanced** page from the tool allows to customize special slideshow settings to use in particular conditions."
msgstr "Stran **Napredno** v orodju omogoča prilagajanje posebnih nastavitev diaprojekcije za uporabo v določenih pogojih."

#: ../../slideshow_tools/presentation_tool.rst:62
msgid "The Advanced Settings from Presentation Tool"
msgstr "Napredne nastavitve iz orodja za predstavitve"

#: ../../slideshow_tools/presentation_tool.rst:64
msgid "During the slide-show, you can access a toolbar on the upper left screen corner. Move the mouse cursor to the top left of the screen to access it."
msgstr ""

#: ../../slideshow_tools/presentation_tool.rst:66
msgid "With this tool bar, you can drive the progress of the slide show. You can pause or play the slide-show, go back to the preview image, go to the next image, and stop the slide-show."
msgstr ""

#: ../../slideshow_tools/presentation_tool.rst:68
msgid "In the lower left screen corner you can see the current image file name, the current image index, and the total number of images included in the slide-show."
msgstr "V spodnjem levem kotu zaslona lahko vidite ime trenutne slikovne datoteke, trenutni indeks slike in skupno število slik, vključenih v diaprojekcijo."

#: ../../slideshow_tools/presentation_tool.rst:75
msgid "Screencast of the Presentation Tool Running With Cube OpenGL Effect and Showing OSD on the Top of Screen"
msgstr "Posnetek predstavitvenega orodja, ki se izvaja z učinkom Cube OpenGL in prikazuje OSD na vrhu zaslona"
